        }
      ],
      "text": "Prior to the battle at Wulong Forest, Toph, Suki, and Sokka arrived at the shore of the island, but realized that they were too late to intercept the fleet. As the airship armada began to depart, Toph launched the trio onto the nearest airship, which they were able to commandeer and use to stage a sabotage of the entire fleet."
